{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTk1Ng_0005","text":"我也許會問候","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["思考","關心","猶豫"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["也許","問候"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,9,2,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","jaa5","heoi2","man6","hau6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"問候","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「也許」一詞帶出不確定性，顯示說話者在考慮是否要聯繫對方。"},"source":{"title":"天蠍號","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1956","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTk1Ng_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTk1Ng_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTk1Ng_0006","text":"祖家的你 渺小的永久","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["距離","渺小","永恆"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["祖家","渺小","永久"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,3,5,5,9,3,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zou2","gaa1","dik1","nei5","miu5","siu2","dik1","wing5","gau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"祖家","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"渺小","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"永久","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"將對方置於「祖家」，並形容其「渺小的永久」，暗示對方在自己眼中微不足道但又似乎是永恆的存在。"},"source":{"title":"天蠍號","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1956","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTk1Ng_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTk1Ng_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
